            "text": "Route 101, which currently runs from Square One to Clarkson GO Station, will be extended south to Port Credit. This means riders heading to the waterfront will no longer need to transfer. The extended route adds approximately twelve minutes to the end-to-end journey but eliminates one transfer. Buses on this route will run every ten minutes during peak hours and every twenty minutes off-peak."
